# Import Rules

## Alias imports

- Prefer alias imports `@/...` across the codebase.

## Component imports

- When importing UI components, prefer **barrels**:
  - `@/components/ui`
  - `@/components/patterns`

Avoid deep imports like `@/components/ui/button` in app code.

## Avoid cycles inside components

- Inside `src/components/ui/**` and `src/components/patterns/**`, prefer **relative imports** when importing other components from those folders (e.g. `../ui`).
- Keep `lib/*` imports as alias (`@/lib/...`).

